{"tid":1511330,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"響葵興食左間藍絲餐廳食到火都起撚埋","createTime":"2019-08-27T13:32:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T17:26:51.000Z","uid":187262,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"4dae33f1ccef376505123f02cfef27352965ada9","tid":1511330,"uid":187262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:32:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ti6ZbM0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTi6ZbM0.png&h=81e55dd2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ct0OPyG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCt0OPyG.png&h=f8639be1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我就812去食嘅<br />\n本身都唔想理<br />\n但我見825荃灣嗰日勁多人去食<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你地以後唔好撚再去</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗰日去間垃圾到食<br />\n間野已經迫到仆街<br />\n之後有個肥佬響到行黎行去<br />\n個屎忽大撚到<br />\n我一路食佢個屎忽就一路響我側邊行黎行去<br />\n聽啲伙記叫佢超哥 應該經理黎<br />\n都算撚數<br />\n之後聽到厨房有個呀姐勁大聲話<br />\n嘩 個後生仔比人按落地下<br />\n面都爛曬喎 嘩門牙都甩埋<br />\n個肥閪即刻勁大聲話<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">抵撚死啦 死暴徒</span><br />\n之後有個後生仔伙記即刻屌翻佢<br />\n點抵死呀？你係咪人黎架 咩立場都唔應該咁講野啦<br />\n(我暗暗讚好)<br />\n之後個肥閪又講左句<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">死暴徒 點解唔抵死呀</span>？<br />\n之後個後生伙記比其他伙記拉住<br />\n就無左件事了<br />\n我當時無做到啲咩<br />\n只係偷偷影左兩張相<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aXP76jf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaXP76jf.png&h=ed76626f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/brTXJ5Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbrTXJ5Z.png&h=4be09e65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係咪真係肥到隻豬咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以後咪撚去食！</span></span>"},{"pid":"dfd82b8f5b89ee7d86052f88e555898ab6678cf3","tid":1511330,"uid":52817,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:32:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NSAWdB2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNSAWdB2.jpg&h=7e1fa5a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0e5171440525f4ea35f4354098c4e71cc27358c3","tid":1511330,"uid":187262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:33:00.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"0854d284bbbabff1f63a5a4e31b4e3f109c3c7c7","tid":1511330,"uid":187262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:33:37.000Z","msg":"推呀屌 葵青撚！"},{"pid":"45c3c7eb8fa1fc101d55c406556eaade541a00a7","tid":1511330,"uid":187262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:34:07.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"3f66ac287b01365158104f07919646985d6f0bfa","tid":1511330,"uid":187262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:34:17.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"a4f0be831827338b5644afbba8fd60f883e8dbc0","tid":1511330,"uid":88578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:34:29.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"aa2b7c188a084a0ec92869a9ed63471bce90e5cd","tid":1511330,"uid":187262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:34:30.000Z","msg":"推3"},{"pid":"b6afa717b8d20904c2695362986c1f87d9893147","tid":1511330,"uid":210612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:34:33.000Z","msg":"食環"},{"pid":"f323f32d0c0cddd27bd3ddeabde841ad3198da12","tid":1511330,"uid":133528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:34:59.000Z","msg":"咁即係間野又黃又藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb33458208f1d73fe3f9e3de74a724bc3c10b4e9","tid":1511330,"uid":143382,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:35:01.000Z","msg":"推 1823"},{"pid":"1bd1c7e3d2b31f186a0eaf25c8d87623f96f8fee","tid":1511330,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:36:01.000Z","msg":"食對面夏面館<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgm